# Changelog

## [0.1.0] - 2024-03-19
### Changed
- Replaced Mapbox with Leaflet + OpenStreetMap
- Added marker management (add/remove/drag)
- Added route visualization using Leaflet Routing Machine
- Added test points feature
- Enhanced UI with shadcn/ui components and styling
- Added proper Tailwind configuration
- Improved modal and button designs
- Added dark mode support
- Enhanced chat message styling

### Added
- Initial project structure setup
- Basic frontend UI with TailwindCSS and Alpine.js
- Express server setup with basic routing
- SQLite database initialization with core tables
- Basic route optimization endpoint
- Mapbox integration for route visualization
- Chat interface for AI interaction

### Technical Details
- Created project directory structure
- Implemented SQLite database schema
- Set up Express server with CORS and basic middleware
- Added frontend with responsive design
- Integrated Mapbox GL JS for map visualization
- Added AI chat interface with Alpine.js
- Implemented basic route optimization logic

### Enhanced
- Added multiple map styles (Basic, Streets, Light, Dark, Satellite)
- Added dark mode support for map and UI
- Removed click-to-add-marker functionality
- Added map style preferences storage
- Added sophisticated route optimization logic
- Implemented persistent instructions handling
- Added fleet management endpoints
- Enhanced AI prompt engineering for better route planning
- Added detailed route plan storage in database
- Improved error handling and response formatting
- Added outlet management with map icons
- Added random order generation (3000 orders)
- Fixed settings modal display
- Added batch processing for large order generation
